text:
There are two typo's in the default PHP included configuration:

1: 
$config['nmap']           = '/usr/localbin/nmap';
Should be
$config['nmap']           = '/usr/local/bin/nmap';

2:
$config['mtr']            = '/usr/local/bin/mtr';
Should be
$config['mtr']            = '/usr/local/sbin/mtr';
